### register full
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/{{prefix}}/auth/register
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@mail.com",
  "password": "admin"
}

### register empty
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/{{prefix}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### login full
