### get me
GET http://localhost:{{port}}/{{prefix}}/auth/current
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### logout
GET http://localhost:{{port}}/{{prefix}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### refresh full
GET http://localhost:{{port}}/{{prefix}}/auth/refresh
